Soloing classes at 60 go approx. depending on circumstances;<br>
chanter(w/dire charm), druid(w/dire charm), necromancer(w/dire charm), shaman/monk(tied for best really), necromancer, druid/wizard(quad kiting), enchanter, sk/pal/bard, War/rog/ranger(there is no telling however what unlimited arrows will do for this class), mage(I would guess that beastlords would fall about were we do). This is all from first hand or commonly accepted information, the classes I have experience with at this level are monk/mage/shaman/cleric/warrior, I have personally witnessed or played(although not to the huge extent I have with the previously listed classes)rogues/rangers/sks/paladins/bards.<br>
<br>
